@Node Compact "Compacted files"

	@{u}@{b}XPK files management@{ub}@{uu}



Searcher recognizes and decompress himself XPK files. For the other packer, the famous MCP have the powerfull CrunchPatch option which unpack packed files automatically. With MCP, IconAct is able to unpack XPK (and others packed format) files automatically.


@EndNode
